# JavaScript Functionality

The NexusAI website includes several JavaScript functions to enhance the user experience.

## Key JavaScript Features

### Navigation
- Mobile menu toggle functionality
- Smooth scrolling for anchor links

### Animations
- Intersection Observer for scroll-based animations
- Terminal typing effect simulation
- Animated display of terminal commands and responses

### Implementation Details
All JavaScript is included at the bottom of the [index.html](mdc:index.html) file in a `<script>` tag. The main functions include:

1. Mobile menu toggle handler
2. Smooth scrolling implementation for navigation links
3. Animation observer for fade-in effects
4. Terminal typing effect with simulated command execution

